2f200 | 3\u202f500 | 6\u202f500 |\\n| **Attractions & activities** (jet\u2011ski, parasailing, kayak, entry fees) | 2\u202f500 | 3\u202f500 | 5\u202f000 |\\n| **Nightlife / drinks** (optional) | 1\u202f000 | 1\u202f500 | 2\u202f500 |\\n| **Misc. (souvenirs, tips, emergency) ** | 1\u202f200 | 1\u202f200 | 1\u202f200 |\\n| **Total** | **\u20b9\u202f11\u202f000** | **\u20b9\u202f22\u202f400** | **\u20b9\u202f46\u202f900** |\\n\\nAll three totals stay comfortably **below the \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000 ceiling**. You can always upgrade a line\u2011item (e.g., add a spa treatment in the luxury tier) and still have a buffer.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 6\ufe0f\u20e3 QUICK\u2011TIP CHECK\u2011LIST  \\n\\n| \u2714\ufe0f | Item |\\n|----|------|\\n| **Travel tickets** | Book train/flight 2\u20113\u202fweeks early. |\\n| **Hotel reservation** | Confirm cancellation policy; request sea\u2011view if possible. |\\n| **Scooter licence** | Carry a valid driving licence; wear a helmet (mandatory). |\\n| **Cash & cards** | Most places accept cards, but keep \u20b9\u202f2\u202f000\u2011\u20b9\u202f3\u202f000 in cash for beach shacks & small vendors. |\\n| **Sun protection** | Sunscreen SPF\u202f30+, hat, sunglasses. |\\n| **Health** | Carry basic meds (painkiller, motion\u2011sickness, water\u2011purifier tablets). |\\n| **Packing** | Light cottons, swimwear, flip\u2011flops, a light jacket for evenings. |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 7\ufe0f\u20e3 SAMPLE DAILY EXPENSE (Mid\u2011range)  \\n\\n| Category | Amount |\\n|----------|--------|\\n| Hotel (2\u202fnights) | \u20b9\u202f7\u202f000 |\\n| Food (\u20b9\u202f1\u202f750\u202f/\u202fday) | \u20b9\u202f3\u202f500 |\\n| Scooter + fuel | \u20b9\u202f700 |\\n| Activities (jet\u2011ski + kayak) | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f200 |\\n| Entry fees & sightseeing | \u20b9\u202f300 |\\n| Nightlife (drinks) | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f500 |\\n| Misc / souvenirs | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f200 |\\n| **Total** | **\u20b9\u202f15\u202f400** (\u2248\u202f30\u202f% of the \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000 budget) |\\n\\nYou still have **\u20b9\u202f34\u202f600** left for upgrades, shopping, or a more comfortable travel mode.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 8\ufe0f\u20e3 FINAL RECOMMENDATION  \\n\\nIf you\u2019re traveling **solo** and want the best value, the **Mid\u2011range** plan (The Flora Residency) gives you a comfortable stay, a mix of beach\u2011action and cultural sights, and still leaves a healthy cash cushion for extra experiences (spa, fine\u2011dining, or a day\u2011trip to **Dudhsagar Falls**).  \\n\\nIf you\u2019re traveling **as a couple** and want to splurge a little, the **Luxury** option at Taj Exotica turns the two nights into a mini\u2011resort escape while still keeping the overall spend under \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000.\\n\\nEnjoy your Goa adventure! \ud83c\udf34\ud83c\udfd6\ufe0f Feel free to ask for any tweaks (e.g., vegetarian food spots, alternative activities, or a 3\u2011day extension).\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"}}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_f468eb2b-dffe-488b-ade5-e2c1090b5c08/f468eb2b-dffe-488b-ade5-e2c1090b5c08", "receiver": "output_topic_f468eb2b-dffe-488b-ade5-e2c1090b5c08/f468eb2b-dffe-488b-ade5-e2c1090b5c08", "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.SEND", "type": "Message"}
2026-02-21 15:11:45 - INFO - 405 -Publishing message of type GroupChatAgentResponse to all subscribers: {'response': Response(chat_message=TextMessage(id='884e31f6-3ef2-4999-9533-9ec4fbda8f03', source='Travel_Planner', models_usage=RequestUsage(prompt_tokens=137, completion_tokens=2317), metadata={}, created_at=datetime.datetime(2026, 2, 21, 9, 41, 45, 982683, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), content='## 2\u2011Day Goa Getaway ľ\u202f\u20b9\u202f50\u202f000 (\u2248\u202f$600)  \n\nBelow is a ready\u2011to\u2011use itinerary that fits three comfort levels ľ **Budget**, **Mid\u2011range** and **Luxury** ľ while staying under the overall cap of \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000.  \nAll prices are **per person** (single occupancy) and shown in Indian Rupees (\u20b9).  \n\n---\n\n## 1\ufe0f\u20e3 QUICK OVERVIEW  \n\n| Day | Main Theme | Key Spots | Approx. Travel Time |\n|-----|------------|-----------|---------------------|\n| **Day\u202f1** | North\u2011Goa beach & culture | Calangute \u2192 Baga \u2192 Fort Aguada \u2192 Candolim \u2192 Sunset at Chapora | 30\u201145\u202fmin between stops |\n| **Day\u202f2** | South\u2011Goa relaxation & nature | Palolem \u2192 Agonda \u2192 Cabo de Rama Fort \u2192 Return to hotel | 1\u20111.5\u202fh between stops |\n\n*All attractions are open daily; most are free or have a small entry fee (\u20b9\u202f20\u2011\u20b9\u202f250).*\n\n---\n\n## 2\ufe0f\u20e3 DETAILED DAY\u2011BY\u2011DAY ITINERARY  \n\n### Day\u202f1 ľ North Goa Vibes  \n\n| Time | Activity | Details / Tips |\n|------|----------|----------------|\n| **08:00** | **Breakfast** | Hotel buffet (incl. in stay) or local cafÚ ľ try Goan *pŃo* with butter & coffee. |\n| **09:00** | **Calangute Beach** | Walk the promenade, rent a **jet\u2011ski** (\u20b9\u202f800\u202f/\u202f30\u202fmin) or just relax. |\n| **11:00** | **Baga & Anjuna Market** | Souvenirs, beachwear, street\u2011food (prawn balchŃo). |\n| **13:00** | **Lunch** | Beach shack ľ **Goan fish thali** (\u20b9\u202f250\u2011\u20b9\u202f350). |\n| **14:30** | **Fort Aguada & Lighthouse** | Entry free; small parking fee (\u20b9\u202f30). Great photo spot. |\n| **16:00** | **Candolim Beach** | Sunset stroll; optional **parasailing** (\u20b9\u202f1\u202f200). |\n| **18:30** | **Dinner** | **Fishermanĺs Wharf** (mid\u2011range) ľ Goan prawn curry, rice (\u20b9\u202f600\u2011\u20b9\u202f800). |\n| **20:30** | **Nightlife** (optional) | **Titoĺs** or **Mamboĺs** ľ drinks \u20b9\u202f300\u2011\u20b9\u202f500 each. |\n| **22:30** | Return to hotel ľ rest. |  |\n\n---\n\n### Day\u202f2 ľ South Goa Serenity  \n\n| Time | Activity | Details / Tips |\n|------|----------|----------------|\n| **07:30** | **Early Breakfast** | Hotel or quick bite (idli\u2011vada, \u20b9\u202f150). |\n| **08:30** | **Drive to Palolem** | 1\u202fh\u202f30\u202fmin via NH66. Scenic coastal road. |\n| **10:30** | **Palolem Beach** | Kayak in the lagoon (\u20b9\u202f400\u202f/\u202fhour) or just sunbathe. |\n| **12:30** | **Lunch** | Beachside shack ľ **Goan chicken xacuti** (\u20b9\u202f300\u2011\u20b9\u202f400). |\n| **14:00** | **Agonda Beach** | Quiet spot; optional **turtle\u2011watching** (seasonal, free). |\n| **16:00** | **Cabo de Rama Fort** | Entry \u20b9\u202f20; panoramic sea view. |\n| **18:00** | **Sunset at Colva / Benaulim** | Quick stop for photo\u2011ops. |\n| **19:30** | **Dinner** | **Martinĺs Corner** (mid\u2011range) ľ seafood platter (\u20b9\u202f800\u2011\u20b9\u202f1\u202f000). |\n| **21:30** | Return to hotel (or head to airport/railway station). |  |\n\n---\n\n## 3\ufe0f\u20e3 ACCOMMODATION OPTIONS  \n\n| Category | Hotel (example) | Location | Avg. Nightly Rate (incl. taxes) | Amenities |\n|----------|----------------|----------|--------------------------------|-----------|\n| **Budget** | **Casa De Goa ľ Guesthouse** | Calangute | **\u20b9\u202f1\u202f200** (double\u2011room, 1\u2011bed) | Free Wi\u2011Fi, rooftop, shared bathroom |\n| **Mid\u2011range** | **The Flora Residency** | Candolim | **\u20b9\u202f3\u202f500** (deluxe, king\u2011bed) | Pool, breakfast, sea view, air\u2011cond |\n| **Luxury** | **Taj Exotica Resort & Spa** | Benaulim (South Goa) | **\u20b9\u202f12\u202f500** (deluxe sea\u2011view) | 5\u2011star service, private beach, spa, all\u2011meals |\n\n*Rates are for **one night**; total for 2 nights = 2\u202fÎ\u202frate. Prices are current (Oct\u202f2024) and may vary slightly with season.*\n\n---\n\n## 4\ufe0f\u20e3 TRANSPORT  \n\n| Mode | Cost (per person) | Notes |\n|------|-------------------|-------|\n| **Round\u2011trip flight** (e.g., Mumbai\u2011Goa) | \u20b9\u202f4\u202f000\u2011\u20b9\u202f6\u202f000 (low\u2011cost carrier) | Book 2\u20113\u202fweeks ahead for best fare. |\n| **Train** (e.g., Mumbai\u202f\u2192\u202fMadgaon) | \u20b9\u202f800\u2011\u20b9\u202f1\u202f200 (2nd\u202fAC) | Overnight, saves a nightĺs hotel. |\n| **Local transport** | **Scooter rental** ľ \u20b9\u202f350\u202f/\u202fday (incl. fuel) <br>**Taxi/auto** ľ \u20b9\u202f200\u2011\u20b9\u202f400 per short ride | Most travelers prefer a scooter for flexibility. |\n| **Airport\u2011to\u2011hotel transfer** | \u20b9\u202f300\u2011\u20b9\u202f500 (pre\u2011booked taxi) | Or use the scooter if youĺre comfortable. |\n\n*Choose the travel\u2011to\u2011Goa option that fits your overall budget; the figures below assume you **arrive by train** (\u20b9\u202f1\u202f000) to keep the total under \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000.*\n\n---\n\n## 5\ufe0f\u20e3 BUDGET BREAKDOWN  \n\n| Item | Budget (\u20b9) | Mid\u2011range (\u20b9) | Luxury (\u20b9) |\n|------|------------|--------------|------------|\n| **Transport to Goa** (train + airport\u2011taxi) | 1\u202f000 | 1\u202f000 | 1\u202f000 |\n| **Local transport** (scooter 2\u202fdays) | 700 | 700 | 700 |\n| **Accommodation** (2\u202fnights) | 2\u202f400 | 7\u202f000 | 25\u202f000 |\n| **Food** (breakfast\u2011lunch\u2011dinner, 2\u202fdays) | 2\u202f200 | 3\u202f500 | 6\u202f500 |\n| **Attractions & activities** (jet\u2011ski, parasailing, kayak, entry fees) | 2\u202f500 | 3\u202f500 | 5\u202f000 |\n| **Nightlife / drinks** (optional) | 1\u202f000 | 1\u202f500 | 2\u202f500 |\n| **Misc. (souvenirs, tips, emergency) ** | 1\u202f200 | 1\u202f200 | 1\u202f200 |\n| **Total** | **\u20b9\u202f11\u202f000** | **\u20b9\u202f22\u202f400** | **\u20b9\u202f46\u202f900** |\n\nAll three totals stay comfortably **below the \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000 ceiling**. You can always upgrade a line\u2011item (e.g., add a spa treatment in the luxury tier) and still have a buffer.\n\n---\n\n## 6\ufe0f\u20e3 QUICK\u2011TIP CHECK\u2011LIST  \n\n| \u2714\ufe0f | Item |\n|----|------|\n| **Travel tickets** | Book train/flight 2\u20113\u202fweeks early. |\n| **Hotel reservation** | Confirm cancellation policy; request sea\u2011view if possible. |\n| **Scooter licence** | Carry a valid driving licence; wear a helmet (mandatory). |\n| **Cash & cards** | Most places accept cards, but keep \u20b9\u202f2\u202f000\u2011\u20b9\u202f3\u202f000 in cash for beach shacks & small vendors. |\n| **Sun protection** | Sunscreen SPF\u202f30+, hat, sunglasses. |\n| **Health** | Carry basic meds (painkiller, motion\u2011sickness, water\u2011purifier tablets). |\n| **Packing** | Light cottons, swimwear, flip\u2011flops, a light jacket for evenings. |\n\n---\n\n## 7\ufe0f\u20e3 SAMPLE DAILY EXPENSE (Mid\u2011range)  \n\n| Category | Amount |\n|----------|--------|\n| Hotel (2\u202fnights) | \u20b9\u202f7\u202f000 |\n| Food (\u20b9\u202f1\u202f750\u202f/\u202fday) | \u20b9\u202f3\u202f500 |\n| Scooter + fuel | \u20b9\u202f700 |\n| Activities (jet\u2011ski + kayak) | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f200 |\n| Entry fees & sightseeing | \u20b9\u202f300 |\n| Nightlife (drinks) | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f500 |\n| Misc / souvenirs | \u20b9\u202f1\u202f200 |\n| **Total** | **\u20b9\u202f15\u202f400** (\u2248\u202f30\u202f% of the \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000 budget) |\n\nYou still have **\u20b9\u202f34\u202f600** left for upgrades, shopping, or a more comfortable travel mode.\n\n---\n\n## 8\ufe0f\u20e3 FINAL RECOMMENDATION  \n\nIf youĺre traveling **solo** and want the best value, the **Mid\u2011range** plan (The Flora Residency) gives you a comfortable stay, a mix of beach\u2011action and cultural sights, and still leaves a healthy cash cushion for extra experiences (spa, fine\u2011dining, or a day\u2011trip to **Dudhsagar Falls**).  \n\nIf youĺre traveling **as a couple** and want to splurge a little, the **Luxury** option at Taj Exotica turns the two nights into a mini\u2011resort escape while still keeping the overall spend under \u20b9\u202f50\u202f000.\n\nEnjoy your Goa adventure! \U0001f334\U0001f3d6\ufe0f Feel free to ask for any tweaks (e.g., vegetarian food spots, alternative activities, or a 3\u2011day extension).', type='TextMessage'), inner_messages=[]), 'name': 'Travel_Planner'}
